Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,您是占卜师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.65,Sub-JP,,0,0,0,,えっと　占い師さんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,右手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.47,Sub-JP,,0,0,0,,右手
